snippet.title: Shin Sangoku Musou VS - Walkthrough part 1
snippet.description:
Well guys i make hard work to present you this shin sangoku musou vs walkthrough. I know quality is low but, i don t have good graphics card to record in good quality. I think quality is normal. Yes its can be better but i do my best to record in this quality. Finaly lets talk about game. Plot in this game its just i guess memories characters about great battles they have. We create character (i already creat it but no show on video) who just our officer and we play mission memories with him and other characters. As in samurai warriors chronicles we can switch characters by touch icom on second screen (btw i don t record second screen because its drop fps too hard but i switch on him sometimes) and its very helpful in battles. So, yeah this is first video and in next part i try fix aspect ratio of the screen. Hope you enjoy this game as im.

Thank you for watching!. If you liked this video, you can press like button, or just subscribe and press bell for don t miss my videos, my posts in community tab. If you want support my channel this is link to donation page https://www.paypal.me/AriousSaintWind All this help my channel grow up and motivate me make new interesting video for you.
